{"tid":1116990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅雨下一家四口出東龍洲捕魚 翻舢舨子死父失蹤","createTime":"2019-04-20T11:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T16:55:39.000Z","uid":41404,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb273a8fe60f9a559e66c8df76952a7aaa4b951","tid":1116990,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"本港今日天氣驟變，天文台先後發出黃色及紅色暴雨警告，但仍有人冒着風雨出海，多人墮海失蹤。下午4時許，一名31歲姓何男子偕父母及妻子駕駛舢舨由將軍澳到東龍洲捕魚，至南堂尾對開期間，雷雨交加，舢舨因風急浪大而翻側，4人全部墮海。水警於上址巡邏期間發現一艘翻轉的舢舨，先後派員救起何母及何妻，而男事主獲救時已陷昏迷，3人事後由救護車送往東區醫院搶救，何男經搶救後最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方、消防、飛行服務隊及海事處人員繼續搜救，暫時未有發現59歲何父，案件列作在香港水域搜救及失蹤人士，行動仍在進行中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190420/59510427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190420%2F59510427&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=ed7cabe7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190420%2F59510427&h=14abc1f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190420/59510427</a>"},{"pid":"9f2948cb0cfa9cf412147442bc57b170a361a119","tid":1116990,"uid":101714,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"朝早出去都可以話天文台預報唔準<br />\n屌你下晝四點幾出海真係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8660ce7d899785f1d0f53fe203eda5036d1f65c8","tid":1116990,"uid":42188,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:30:34.000Z","msg":"RIP, 口德+100分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181d9900e1e9a8979d48ea608eedbbea248b5f9d","tid":1116990,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T11:31:37.000